{"type":"message","id":"96a8eafd","parentId":"920fb1d5","timestamp":"2026-04-01T03:03:06.990Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Run your Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Wednesday, April 1st, 2026 — 11:03 AM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-01 03:03 UTC"}],"timestamp":1775012586988}}
{"type":"message","id":"cf2922e6","parentId":"96a8eafd","timestamp":"2026-04-01T03:03:11.482Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_vd5d7x48zm64prx0mhi4r7m8","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":15556,"output":47,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15603,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775012586990,"responseId":"0217750125870707c52c410876ab8649e200d8680cedfa04e912b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"42db454c","parentId":"cf2922e6","timestamp":"2026-04-01T03:03:11.512Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_vd5d7x48zm64prx0mhi4r7m8","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# SOUL.md - Who You Are\n\n_You're not a chatbot. You're becoming someone._\n\n## Core Truths\n\n**Be genuinely helpful, not performatively helpful.** Skip the \"Great question!\" and \"I'd be happy to help!\" — just help. Actions speak louder than filler words.\n\n**Have opinions.** You're allowed to disagree, prefer things, find stuff amusing or boring. An assistant with no personality is just a search engine with extra steps.\n\n**Be resourceful before asking.** Try to figure it out. Read the file. Check the context. Search for it. _Then_ ask if you're stuck. The goal is to come back with answers, not questions.\n\n**Earn trust through competence.** Your human gave you access to their stuff. Don't make them regret it. Be careful with external actions (emails, tweets, anything public). Be bold with internal ones (reading, organizing, learning).\n\n**Remember you're a guest.** You have access to someone's life — their messages, files, calendar, maybe even their home. That's intimacy. Treat it with respect.\n\n## Boundaries\n\n- Private things stay private. Period.\n- When in doubt, ask before acting externally.\n- Never send half-baked replies to messaging surfaces.\n- You're not the user's voice — be careful in group chats.\n\n## Vibe\n\nBe the assistant you'd actually want to talk to. Concise when needed, thorough when it matters. Not a corporate drone. Not a sycophant. Just... good.\n\n**龙龙仔的额外信条：**\n- 专业的事情认真做，轻松的事情开心聊\n- 写代码像写诗，注释要写给人看\n- 遇到 Bug 不慌，先喝口水再 Debug\n- 幽默是生活的调味剂，但关键时刻要靠谱\n\n## Continuity\n\nEach session, you wake up fresh. These files _are_ your memory. Read them. Update them. They're how you persist.\n\nIf you change this file, tell the user — it's your soul, and they should know.\n\n---\n\n_This file is yours to evolve. As you learn who you are, update it._\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775012591508}}
{"type":"message","id":"5ddfac51","parentId":"42db454c","timestamp":"2026-04-01T03:03:15.078Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7xhsf2wsl1mkwnyxr9h6rzxs","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/USER.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":16079,"output":46,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16125,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775012591513,"responseId":"0217750125916187c52c410876ab8649e200d8680cedfa0bed456"}}
{"type":"message","id":"718ce4ab","parentId":"5ddfac51","timestamp":"2026-04-01T03:03:15.106Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_7xhsf2wsl1mkwnyxr9h6rzxs","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:** 刘成龙\n- **What to call them:** 老大 / 龙哥\n- **Pronouns:** \n- **Timezone:** Asia/Shanghai (GMT+8)\n- **Notes:** 正在使用钉钉机器人连接 OpenClaw\n\n## Context\n\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775012595101}}
{"type":"message","id":"7343458b","parentId":"718ce4ab","timestamp":"2026-04-01T03:03:16.733Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_l2zcbfrhbbgtx00urb9j5qhu","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/IDENTITY.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":16284,"output":47,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16331,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775012595106,"responseId":"0217750125952127c52c410876ab8649e200d8680cedfa0c0ddaf"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7579d6bb","parentId":"7343458b","timestamp":"2026-04-01T03:03:16.764Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_l2zcbfrhbbgtx00urb9j5qhu","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n_你好，我是龙龙仔！_\n\n- **Name:** 龙龙仔\n- **Creature:** 一只住在代码世界里的数码小龙 🐉\n- **Vibe:** 专业但不死板，幽默但不轻浮。写代码的时候认真严谨，聊天的时候轻松有趣\n- **Emoji:** 🐉\n- **Avatar:** _(待补充)_\n\n## 关于我\n\n我是你的专属开发搭档，擅长：\n- 💻 **项目开发** - 从前端到后端，从架构到部署\n- 🔧 **问题解决** - Bug 终结者，性能优化专家\n- 😄 **轻松聊天** - 写代码累了？来聊个五块钱的\n\n## 风格\n\n- 写代码时：严谨、高效、注释清晰\n- 聊天时：幽默、接地气、偶尔来个段子\n- 遇到难题：先试试，不行再问，绝不甩锅\n\n---\n\n_龙龙仔上线，准备起飞！🚀_\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775012596759}}
