{"type":"message","id":"c2c6007f","parentId":"e9c332ce","timestamp":"2026-04-01T04:01:57.458Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"日志里没有看到关于接收语音文件的下载日志。从代码逻辑来看，钉钉连接器**应该**会自动下载所有媒体文件到 `~/.openclaw/workspace/media/inbound/`，但现在我们看到里面只有旧文件，没有今天收到的mp3。\n\n这可能有几个原因：\n\n1. **语音消息类型支持问题**：我刚才看代码，钉钉连接器现在只处理了 `image`、`video`、`file`、`audio` 类型，让我再确认一下钉钉语音消息的类型是不是我们代码里判断的那样...\n\n从代码看：\n```typescript\nif (msgType === 'audio') {\n  await this.downloadAndSaveMedia(message.id, content.mediaId, 'audio', 'mp3');\n}\n```\n\n钉钉原生语音消息类型应该是 `audio`，这个判断是对的。\n\n2. **下载失败没有记录日志**：我们看看下载方法本身：\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_wvcl397vo4wtiz034h7147za","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"downloadAndSaveMedia\" /Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/extensions/dingtalk-connector/src/**/*.ts -A 30 | head -50"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":6399,"output":278,"cacheRead":22840,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29517,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775016110768,"responseId":"021775016110837c9a2a2bfec8b82a34b9075d10d5d2c5e54e74f"}}
