{"type":"compaction","id":"24f862e1","parentId":"4cac8696","timestamp":"2026-04-01T06:02:01.272Z","summary":"## Decisions\n- 使用summarize技能处理音频转文字: 用户的音频文字提取请求符合该技能的使用场景\n- 先查找目标音频文件位置再进行处理: 全局查找超时终止后，优先检查常见下载目录\n- **Systematically searched common download locations, temporary folders, DingTalk cache directories and entire disk to locate the file**: After initial checks failed, expanded search scope systematically\n- **Request manual save**: Advised user to manually save the audio to the Downloads folder when automatic search failed\n- **Determined cross-machine access issue**: Confirmed that the file is on a different machine than the one the assistant is connected to, so direct access is impossible\n- **Expanded full disk search**: Ran full disk search for `*F82*.mp3` to locate the target file after targeted searches failed\n- **Searched recent DingTalk container MP3s**: Checked DingTalk container directories for MP3 files downloaded in the last 1 day after full disk search found no results\n- **查看钉钉连接器源代码**: 需要检查接收文件的处理逻辑\n- **已读取核心入口文件 `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/extensions/dingtalk-connector/src/core/provider.ts`**: 查看核心接收文件逻辑与钉钉消息流协调逻辑\n- **接下来查看消息处理文件 `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/extensions/dingtalk-connector/src/core/message-handler.ts`**: 定位文件下载处理逻辑\n- **查找默认接收文件目录**: 根据代码推测文件应保存到 `agentWorkspaceDir/media/inbound`，执行查找确认目录位置\n- After failing to find download logic in `download-manager.ts` and `provider.ts`, decided to check `message-handler.ts` next\n- **Identified root logic cause**: The existing conditional skips audio file persistence for voice messages that have automatic ASR text, which is the default behavior of DingTalk\n- **Fix logic change**: For audio files, always save the file to local disk regardless of whether DingTalk provides built-in speech recognition text, only change how text is appended to the message (don't add extra text for downloaded audio files when recognition exists)\n- **Updated file type check**: Expand audio file detection