{"type":"message","id":"b65613ca","parentId":"40c90db0","timestamp":"2026-04-01T06:02:20.981Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"太好了！从日志里看到**钉钉连接器确实收到了消息**：`统计：收到=1, 处理=1`，处理成功了！让我们看看 inbound 目录有没有新文件下来：\n\n\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_zfvoknmcgcejs03h7obt00zo","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -lt /Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/media/inbound/ | head -10"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":29914,"output":99,"cacheRead":1848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31861,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775023330678,"responseId":"0217750233308028e13156721812cf3aa873c08415dc3f4e6ea17"}}
