{"type":"message","id":"bcdd2864","parentId":"5ef1d2da","timestamp":"2026-04-01T06:03:17.359Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"找到了！找到了！下载处理在这里，然后：\n\n```typescript\nfor (let i = 0; i < content.downloadCodes.length; i++) {\n  const code = content.downloadCodes[i];\n  const fileName = content.fileNames[i];\n  if (!fileName) {\n    // ...处理图片，忽略其他类型\n  }\n  // 那有 fileName 的非图片去哪里了？？？哦！根本没下载！！\n}\n```\n\n问题终于找到了！现在代码里只处理 `!fileName` 的图片下载，有 `fileName` 的音频、视频、文件根本不处理！！所以 `downloadCodes` 收集了，但是没下载！\n\n我们修复一下这个逻辑：把 `!fileName` 改成只有文件名匹配图片的时候才处理，对于音频、视频、普通文件，都下载：\n\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1y48wok2p14r0yg9hw9kkkk1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/extensions/dingtalk-connector/src/core/message-handler.ts","offset":790,"limit":50}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":5700,"output":265,"cacheRead":23864,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29829,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775023391957,"responseId":"0217750233920878e13156721812cf3aa873c08415dc3f42b875c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e9fb55fd","parentId":"bcdd2864","timestamp":"2026-04-01T06:03:17.394Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1y48wok2p14r0yg9hw9kkkk1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n  // 处理 downloadCodes（来自 picture 消息，fileNames 为空的是图片）\n  for (let i = 0; i < content.downloadCodes.length; i++) {\n    const code = content.downloadCodes[i];\n    const fileName = content.fileNames[i];\n    if (!fileName) {\n      try {\n        log?.info?.(`处理 downloadCode 图片 ${i + 1}/${content.downloadCodes.length}`);\n        const localPath = await downloadMediaByCode(code, config, agentWorkspaceDir, log);\n        if (localPath) {\n          imageLocalPaths.push(localPath);\n          log?.info?.(`downloadCode 图片下载成功 ${i + 1}/${content.downloadCodes.length}`);\n        } else {\n          log?.warn?.(`downloadCode 图片下载失败 ${i + 1}/${content.downloadCodes.length}`);\n        }\n      } catch (err: any) {\n        log?.error?.(`downloadCode 图片下载异常 ${i + 1}/${content.downloadCodes.length}: ${err.message}`);\n      }\n    }\n  }\n  \n  log?.info?.(`图片下载完成: 成功=${imageLocalPaths.length}, 总数=${content.imageUrls.length + content.downloadCodes.filter((_, i) => !content.fileNames[i]).length}`);\n\n\n\n  // ===== 文件附件处理：自动下载并解析内容 =====\n  const fileContentParts: string[] = [];\n  for (let i = 0; i < content.downloadCodes.length; i++) {\n    const code = content.downloadCodes[i];\n    const fileName = content.fileNames[i];\n    if (!fileName) continue;\n\n    try {\n      log?.info?.(`处理文件附件 ${i + 1}/${content.downloadCodes.length}: ${fileName}`);\n      \n      // 获取下载链接\n      const downloadUrl = await getFileDownloadUrl(code, fileName, config, log);\n      if (!downloadUrl) {\n        fileContentParts.push(`⚠️ 文件获取失败: ${fileName}`);\n        continue;\n      }\n\n      // 下载文件到本地\n      const localPath = await downloadFileToLocal(downloadUrl, fileName, agentWorkspaceDir, log);\n      if (!localPath) {\n        fileContentParts.push(`⚠️ 文件下载失败: ${fileName}\\n🔗 [点击下载](${downloadUrl})`);\n        continue;\n      }\n\n      // 识别文件类型\n\n[458 more lines in file. Use offset=840 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775023397390}}
{"type":"message","id":"633aca65","parentId":"e9fb55fd","timestamp":"2026-04-01T06:03:22.184Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"太好了！下面还有 `fileContentParts` 的处理！在这之后，`for (let i = 0; ... content.downloadCodes.length; i++)`，对 **有 fileName 的都处理了**！\n\n但是问题是什么呢？我们先看看现在怎么判断文件类型的：\n\n\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4z0dgbyj06573j9lovbh1zgz","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/extensions/dingtalk-connector/src/core/message-handler.ts","offset":815,"limit":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":3465,"output":147,"cacheRead":26936,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30548,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775023397396,"responseId":"0217750233975288e13156721812cf3aa873c08415dc3f4ff7c84"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3f1c7370","parentId":"633aca65","timestamp":"2026-04-01T06:03:22.219Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_4z0dgbyj06573j9lovbh1zgz","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"  // ===== 文件附件处理：自动下载并解析内容 =====\n  const fileContentParts: string[] = [];\n  for (let i = 0; i < content.downloadCodes.length; i++) {\n    const code = content.downloadCodes[i];\n    const fileName = content.fileNames[i];\n    if (!fileName) continue;\n\n    try {\n      log?.info?.(`处理文件附件 ${i + 1}/${content.downloadCodes.length}: ${fileName}`);\n      \n      // 获取下载链接\n      const downloadUrl = await getFileDownloadUrl(code, fileName, config, log);\n      if (!downloadUrl) {\n        fileContentParts.push(`⚠️ 文件获取失败: ${fileName}`);\n        continue;\n      }\n\n      // 下载文件到本地\n      const localPath = await downloadFileToLocal(downloadUrl, fileName, agentWorkspaceDir, log);\n      if (!localPath) {\n        fileContentParts.push(`⚠️ 文件下载失败: ${fileName}\\n🔗 [点击下载](${downloadUrl})`);\n        continue;\n      }\n\n      // 识别文件类型\n      const ext = path.extname(fileName).toLowerCase();\n      let fileType = '文件';\n      \n      if (['.mp4', '.avi', '.mov', '.mkv', '.flv', '.wmv', '.webm'].includes(ext)) {\n        fileType = '视频';\n      } else if (['.mp3', '.wav', '.aac', '.ogg', '.m4a', '.flac', '.wma', '.amr'].includes(ext)) {\n        fileType = '音频';\n      } else if (['.jpg', '.jpeg', '.png', '.gif', '.bmp', '.webp'].includes(ext)) {\n        fileType = '图片';\n      } else if (['.txt', '.md', '.json', '.xml', '.yaml', '.yml', '.csv', '.log', '.js', '.ts', '.py', '.java', '.c', '.cpp', '.h', '.sh', '.bat'].includes(ext)) {\n        fileType = '文本文件';\n      } else if (['.docx', '.doc'].includes(ext)) {\n        fileType = 'Word 文档';\n      } else if (ext === '.pdf') {\n        fileType = 'PDF 文档';\n      } else if (['.xlsx', '.xls'].includes(ext)) {\n        fileType = 'Excel 表格';\n      } else if (['.pptx', '.ppt'].includes(ext)) {\n        fileType = 'PPT 演示文稿';\n      } else if (['.zip', '.rar', '.7z', '.tar', '.gz'].includes(ext)) {\n        fileType = '压缩包';\n      }\n\n      // 解析文件内容\n      const parseResult = await parseFileContent(localPath, fileName, log);\n      \n      if (parseResult.type === 'text' && parseResult.content) {\n        // 文本类文件：将内容注入到上下文（即使解析成功也给出文件路径）\n        const contentPreview = parseResult.content.length > 200 \n          ? parseResult.content.slice(0, 200) + '...' \n          : parseResult.content;\n        \n        fileContentParts.push(\n          `📄 **${fileType}**: ${fileName}\\n` +\n          `✅ 已解析文件内容（${parseResult.content.length} 字符）\\n` +\n\n[423 more lines in file. Use offset=875 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775023402215}}
{"type":"message","id":"2a8b70b9","parentId":"3f1c7370","timestamp":"2026-04-01T06:03:31.980Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"看到了，现在扩展名判断已经包含了 `.amr`！完美！那问题就是，刚才在 `richText` 的处理中，我们给音频默认文件名是 `audio` 而不是 `audio.amr`！所以扩展名是空，不会被识别为音频，也不会保存？不对 —— 代码会下载，因为不管是什么文件类型，只要有 fileName 就会走 `getFileDownloadUrl -> downloadFileToLocal`，只是无法解析内容，但是文件肯定会下载下来啊！\n\n那为什么文件名会没有扩展名？看这里：\n```typescript\n// 处理音频\nif (part.type === 'audio' && part.downloadCode) {\n  downloadCodes.push(part.downloadCode);\n  fileNames.push(part.fileName || 'audio');\n}\n```\n当 part.fileName 不存在的时候，默认给了 `audio`，不是 `audio.amr`！我们把默认名称改对：\n\n\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_w3i2cj97blyxysx0uhxp2i8i","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/extensions/dingtalk-connector/src/core/message-handler.ts","oldText":"        // 处理音频\n        if (part.type === 'audio' && part.downloadCode) {\n          downloadCodes.push(part.downloadCode);\n          fileNames.push(part.fileName || 'audio');\n        }","newText":"        // 处理音频\n        if (part.type === 'audio' && part.downloadCode) {\n          downloadCodes.push(part.downloadCode);\n          fileNames.push(part.fileName || 'audio.amr');\n        }"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":6305,"output":381,"cacheRead":24376,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31062,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775023402220,"responseId":"0217750234023518e13156721812cf3aa873c08415dc3f4ae5ea5"}}
